==Sister cities==
Lucca is twinned with:

* Abingdon, England, United Kingdom
* Colmar, France
* Gorinchem, The Netherlands
* Hämeenlinna, Finland
* Schongau, Germany
* Sint-Niklaas, Belgium
* South San Francisco, United States
