=== Distribution of point values ===
Consider pink noise of any dimension that is produced by generating a Gaussian white noise signal with mean formula_15 and sd formula_16, then multiplying its spectrum with a filter (equivalent to spatially filtering it with a filter formula_17). Then the point values of the pink noise signal will also be normally distributed, with mean formula_15 and sd formula_19.

